  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Retro FPS!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/761250979d33f30fa11a60546911635a.avif?t=1772361117\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Doomed Hell 64 is a retro FPS where you battle through hellish levels filled with monsters and chaos. Battle through endless waves, discover the hidden secrets of hell, and obliterate all living forms!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/b6000044b6bac0c2bbeb7e0237804550.webp?t=1772361117\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/26f030db9c0b6795db8c9929090d09a9.poster.avif?t=1772361117\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/26f030db9c0b6795db8c9929090d09a9.webm?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/26f030db9c0b6795db8c9929090d09a9.mp4?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Doomed Hell 64</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Doomed Hell 64 is a retro old school FPS dungeon crawler that throws you into the depths of a chaotic, monster-infested hell. Fight your way through intense levels in campaign mode, face off against endless waves of enemies, and challenge yourself in various modes, including Arcade and Deadly Race. With procedurally generated scenarios, fast-paced combat, and a wide selection of powerful weapons, every battle feels fresh and full of adrenaline!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/507a323ef4e7e214a5b0a72bc3080c90.webp?t=1772361117\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/dec52712c97bcefe1801a19d7438acea.poster.avif?t=1772361117\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/dec52712c97bcefe1801a19d7438acea.webm?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/dec52712c97bcefe1801a19d7438acea.mp4?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover hidden secrets scattered throughout the levels and unlock over 15 unique upgrades to enhance your gameplay. Customize your arsenal with more than 25 weapon skins, and prepare for fierce encounters with terrifying bosses. Whether you're hunting for easter eggs or obliterating enemies in survival mode, Doomed Hell 64 promises non-stop action and endless replayability!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Doomed Hell 64 is a retro FPS where you battle through hellish levels filled with monsters and chaos. Battle through endless waves, discover the hidden secrets of hell, and obliterate all living forms!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/b6000044b6bac0c2bbeb7e0237804550.webp?t=1772361117\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/26f030db9c0b6795db8c9929090d09a9.poster.avif?t=1772361117\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/26f030db9c0b6795db8c9929090d09a9.webm?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/26f030db9c0b6795db8c9929090d09a9.mp4?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Doomed Hell 64</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Doomed Hell 64 is a retro old school FPS dungeon crawler that throws you into the depths of a chaotic, monster-infested hell. Fight your way through intense levels in campaign mode, face off against endless waves of enemies, and challenge yourself in various modes, including Arcade and Deadly Race. With procedurally generated scenarios, fast-paced combat, and a wide selection of powerful weapons, every battle feels fresh and full of adrenaline!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/507a323ef4e7e214a5b0a72bc3080c90.webp?t=1772361117\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/dec52712c97bcefe1801a19d7438acea.poster.avif?t=1772361117\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/dec52712c97bcefe1801a19d7438acea.webm?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/dec52712c97bcefe1801a19d7438acea.mp4?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover hidden secrets scattered throughout the levels and unlock over 15 unique upgrades to enhance your gameplay. Customize your arsenal with more than 25 weapon skins, and prepare for fierce encounters with terrifying bosses. Whether you're hunting for easter eggs or obliterating enemies in survival mode, Doomed Hell 64 promises non-stop action and endless replayability!</p>",
